h2: Welcome to the Electronics and Computer Science (ECS) Society website. We are a student-run society for ECS at the University of Southampton. On this website you will find information about the society such as who we are, what we aim to do, as well as what events we are currently organising! Still reading? You can even find out more about us.To keep up with the latest events, join the ECSS Facebook group and follow us on Twitter, @ECS_Society.
